{"vv1:0.1":"Vimanavatthu ","vv1:0.2":"Itthivimana ","vv1:0.3":"Pithavagga ","vv1:0.4":"1. Pathamapithavimanavatthu ","vv1:1.1":"Namo tassa Bhagavato Arahato Sammasambuddhassa. ","vv1:2.1":"“Pitham te sovannamayam ularam, ","vv1:2.2":"Manojavam gacchati yenakamam; ","vv1:2.3":"Alankate malyadhare suvatthe, ","vv1:2.4":"Obhasasi vijjurivabbhakutam. ","vv1:3.1":"Kena tetadiso vanno, ","vv1:3.2":"kena te idha mijjhati; ","vv1:3.3":"Uppajjanti ca te bhoga, ","vv1:3.4":"ye keci manaso piya. ","vv1:4.1":"Pucchami tam devi mahanubhave, ","vv1:4.2":"Manussabhuta kimakasi punnam; ","vv1:4.3":"Kenasi evam jalitanubhava, ","vv1:4.4":"Vanno ca te sabbadisa pabhasati”ti. ","vv1:5.1":"Sa devata attamana, ","vv1:5.2":"moggallanena pucchita; ","vv1:5.3":"Panham puttha viyakasi, ","vv1:5.4":"yassa kammassidam phalam. ","vv1:6.1":"“Aham manussesu manussabhuta, ","vv1:6.2":"Abbhagatanasanakam adasim; ","vv1:6.3":"Abhivadayim anjalikam akasim, ","vv1:6.4":"Yathanubhavanca adasi danam. ","vv1:7.1":"Tena metadiso vanno, ","vv1:7.2":"tena me idha mijjhati; ","vv1:7.3":"Uppajjanti ca me bhoga, ","vv1:7.4":"ye keci manaso piya. ","vv1:8.1":"Akkhami te bhikkhu mahanubhava, ","vv1:8.2":"Manussabhuta yamakasi punnam; ","vv1:8.3":"Tenamhi evam jalitanubhava, ","vv1:8.4":"Vanno ca me sabbadisa pabhasati”ti. ","vv1:9.1":"Pathamapithavimanam pathamam. "}